name: KINANTHI#1
description: So the spirit of being wise and wise in doing anything in this universe is the basis of thinking about this works of art that I make. through the figure of a mother as a symbol of a mother's figure here is described as a supernatural power which has an important role to balance the condition of a nature/universe. In Javanese philosophy, we know Jagat Alit / the small universe in the form of ourselves. and Jagat Ageng/universe as a whole. these two things are interconnected in various aspects. so let's build civilization together more wisely.
